{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_87","type":"agent_message","text":"The Groovy internals make the key constraint explicit: once `AssertParameter.notNull(Object, Class)` is hit, Groovy always tries to JIT a static call-site class for `Class.getSimpleName()`. That means a metadata-only fix is a dead end here, so I’m switching to a test-harness shadow of `AssertParameter` in `src/test/java`, which this repo already places ahead of dependency jars on the image classpath."}}
